We are shocked today to hear the news of the passing of legendary drag pioneer and longtime friend of the show Heklina. We have very limited information at this time, but will update you as we know more.  Heklina has been an icon in the drag community and will forever be a legend in San Francisco.  For years Heklina made listeners of the show laugh with her biting sense of humor during her raucous guest appearances. Heklina was probably best known to many as Dorothy in her annual appearance in the San Francisco holiday tradition Golden Girls Live. Our hearts go out to all her friends and family and to the countless fans she made laugh.
To the only person I ever let put me in drag, there are so many things I have to say to you, but I think I’ll just say ‘Thank you for being a friend….’
